    "en": {
      "title": "Apologized miserly",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been reported that the ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of petrol to the country may be further delayed.",
        "Accordingly, the new date will be announced later, said Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekera.",
        "Suppliers assured the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation that the ship would arrive in Sri Lanka yesterday.",
        "The Energy Minister said in a Twitter post that he apologized to the public for the delay. (a)"
      ],
